        <updateDate>2024-07-25T12:59:20Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upskilling and Retraining Assistance Act&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill increases to $12,000 in 2024-2025, the exclusion from employee gross income, for income tax purposes, of employer-paid educational assistance programs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also expands the exclusion to include amounts paid for education-related tools and technology (e.g., hand tools, computers, software, licensure fees).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
